<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170573512268">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170573439551">
<p id="fs-id1170573439554">Sketch the graph of the function <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> with properties i. through vii.</p>
<ol id="fs-id1170573397517" type="i">
<li>The domain of <em data-effect="italics">f</em> is <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mtext>&#8722;</mtext><mi>&#8734;</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>+</mtext><mi>&#8734;</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mtext>&#8722;</mtext><mi>&#8734;</mi><mo>,</mo><mtext>+</mtext><mi>&#8734;</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></li>
